snippet.title: Elon Musk Speaks On Siding With Johnny Depp And Testifying Against Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Speaks On Siding With Johnny Depp And Testifying Against Amber Heard 
Did you know the world's richest man Elon Musk once challenged Johnny Depp to a cage fight? And now, he has to testify against ex Amber Heard? Well, now you know. According to US Weekly, Johnny De6pp and Amber Heard’s legal battle against each other will now involve Elon Musk and actor James Franco who have both been listed as testifiers. The publication cites a court document ordering Musk and Franco to both “produce the books, record, electronically stored information and tangible things designated and described” — including “verbal conversations, telephone calls, letters, emails, memoranda [and] reports — by January 17, 2022.” The documents further request that any communications between the two men and Heard, relating to injuries or harm caused by alleged domestic violence during her marriage to Depp be turned over to the court.
